<p>英 /'vɪzɪt/    美 /'vɪzɪt/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>访问；探望；游览；逗留：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a short-term visit to the UK
到英国的短期旅行</p><footer>2010 福建</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="pay-a-visit-to">pay a visit to</h3>
<p>1.<strong>参观；访问；拜访：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>If you have time, pay a visit to the local museum.
你若有空，参观一下当地的这家博物馆。</p></div></div>